Steps to keep in mind:

1. get a website ready https://themewagon.com/theme-tag/travel-tourism/
2. get your widget folder - copy the 3 files
3. unzip your website inside a xampp/htdocs/abcwebsite-folder
4. copy the 3 flight widget files into the direct src
5. view on the browser
6. duplicate index.html to index.php
7. follow the instruction in the flight.widget.php and copy into index.php
8. run xampp
9. open index.php in browser localhost/(name-of-folder)

